The evidence with the title 'The American Middle Class is losing ground | Pew Research Center ' says Dec 9, 2015  ... And middle-income Americans have fallen further behind financially in the new century. In 2014, the median income of these households was 4% less than in 2000. Moreover, because of the housing market crisis and the Great Recession Of 2007-09, their median wealth (assets minus debts) fell by 28% ... 
